{"tid":1966771,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Android手足有福了！ 華為推 Huawei Card 實體信用卡","createTime":"2020-04-10T11:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T02:14:32.000Z","uid":104138,"like":3,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe8d9daf979f3ed214bd4732991d129c83a641b","tid":1966771,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"華為今日（9日）宣佈，於全球市場推出旗艦手機 P40 系列，同時宣佈夥拍銀聯，在中國境內市場推出 HUAWEI Card 信用卡服務。<br />\n<br />\n華為是次夥拍銀聯合作發行信用卡服務，以 HUAWEI Pay 為基礎，推出手機電子信用卡產品 HUAWEI Card，跟 Apple 同樣提供實體卡片與虛擬卡片兩種使用模式。<br />\n<br />\n跟 Apple Card 一樣，用戶只要直接利用手機內的錢包 APP 即可快速申請及開通，而成功開通後可同步到 HUAWEI Pay 服務。同樣，HUAWEI Card 的每筆消費都可以在錢包 App 當中查看。<br />\n<br />\n卡面與 Apple Card 一樣，僅顯示持卡人個人姓名，不過 HUAWEI Card 採用黑色配襯金色印字，更添奢華感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/hc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fhc1.jpg&h=6836a5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHUAWEI Card 提供消費現金回贈、機場和高鐵等場所貴賓禮遇服務、節日消費特惠，以及華為應用 VIP 禮包等，現時申請免首年年費，惟目前只在中國境內市場推出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/hc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fhc2.jpg&h=e6b9a23b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/04/09/huawei-card/life-tech/epayment/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2Fhuawei-card%2Flife-tech%2Fepayment%2F&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi61SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=348e5977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/04/09/huawei-card/life-tech/epayment/</a>"},{"pid":"56ffa04429ab6d58a7ebce7550e9390ad1746d02","tid":1966771,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T11:58:32.000Z","msg":"有冇手足知點申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{